<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA65">
<l>kalantu naliyuṅ kaṭuntuyarai neñcē</l>
<l>malaṅka vaṭittu maṭippāṉ vilaṅkalpōṟ</l>
<l>ṟoṉmālaik kēcavaṉai nāraṇaṉai mātavaṉai</l>
<l>coṉmālai yeppoḻutuñ cūṭṭu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The severe sorrow that mixes with [and] afflicts us, heart,</l>
<l>he will fatally overcome and fold it up. Always</l>
<l>wear a word garland for mountain-like old Māl,</l>
<l>for Kēcavaṉ, for Nāraṇaṉ, for Mātavaṉ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
